<!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://members.rogers.com/shadowgovernment01/paxil.jpg" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccb9b><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub228.ezboard.com/bxevserverboards.showUserPublicProfile?gid=aerdor>Aerdor</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered Member</span><br>  Posts: 30<br> <font color=#330000>(7/28/03 10:57 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub228.ezboard.com/fxevserverboardsfrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=883.topic&index=56>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: </span><hr size=1> Here's a point for all of you, no matter what side you're on.<br>
